com.ibm.wsdl.extensions
Class PopulatedExtensionRegistry

java.lang.Object
  javax.wsdl.extensions.ExtensionRegistry
      com.ibm.wsdl.extensions.PopulatedExtensionRegistry
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class PopulatedExtensionRegistry
extends ExtensionRegistry

This class extends ExtensionRegistry and pre-registers serializers/deserializers for the SOAP, HTTP and MIME extensions. Java extensionTypes are also mapped for all the SOAP, HTTP and MIME extensions.

Author:
Matthew J. Duftler (duftler@us.ibm.com)
